  "summary": "Easy to make stool utilizing one 12\" wide board.",
  "description": "Easy to make stool utilizing one 12\" wide board. Modified the Kreg Kids' Step Stool to reduce the number of pieces of wood that needed to be joined. Constructed three stools, one for each grandchild, and one for our home. Added grandkids' initials to each end to personalize.",
