  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Cut the side pieces",
      "body": "Cut (2) side pieces - 11 1/4\" x 11\". Cut 2 1/4\" radius' to the upper edges with a jig saw. Cut a 3 1/2\" radius centered on the bottom edge with a jig saw. Use a router to create the hand holes. Use spindle sander to sand the radius' and the hand hold. Round over all edges except the bottom 'feet' with a router round over bit.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/567ffb8c2838d094.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Cut the seat/step",
      "body": "Cut one seat/step piece - 9 1/4\" x 12 1/2\". Use a pocket hole jig to drill pocket holes as shown. Round over the 0utside edges with a router round over bit.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/902b04f3bcabdf31.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Cut the seat/step supports",
      "body": "Cut (2) 2\" x 12 1/2\" x 3/4\" step/seat supports. Use a pocket hole jig to drill the holes as shown. Round over the bottom edge with a router round over bit.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/9ba47c639a37b290.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Assemble the parts - support 1",
      "body": "Secure one support as shown with 1/4\" pocket hole screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/fa3fd7f17460e206.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Assemble the parts - support 2",
      "body": "Secure one support as shown with 1/4\" pocket hole screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/82171628fb9e7116.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Assemble the parts - end piece",
      "body": "Add the final side piece and secure with 1 1/4\" pocket hole screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/d446fbc167252542.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Add the seat",
      "body": "Add the seat and secure to the side pieces with 1 1/4\" pocket hole screws. Also screw the supports to the seat with 1 1/4\" pocket hole screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/3217788b8b02276f.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Paint or Stain the step stool",
      "body": "With assembly complete, paint or stain as desired. Also add floor protection to the bottom of each foot. I used a 1/2\" x 1 3/4\" piece of 1/8\" cork on each foot.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/465cc9d58c95c238.webp"
    }
  ],
